Dubai to Start Quarterly Consumer Confidence Index, WAM Says

-- B y   D a n a   E l   B a l t a j i
-- 
2011-09-14T04:55:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-14/dubai-to-start-quarterly-consumer-confidence-index-wam-says.html
Dubai plans to start a quarterly
consumer confidence index to gauge spending patterns and
household incomes in the emirate, state-run news agency  WAM  said
yesterday.  The Department of  Economic Development  plans to publish its
first report by the end of the fourth quarter of 2011, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dana El Baltaji in Dubai at 
 delbaltaji@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  